    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Those two days are weekends, so it's understandable why this would occur. If a task \"can be completed on the same business day\" but is requested on a weekend, it won't be completed until Monday. This behaviour appears to be intended, according to the following test\r\nhttps://github.com/pandas-dev/pandas/blob/8af8cdbc251c6268fc02a5af9b18e9196a9b6067/pandas/tests/tseries/offsets/test_offsets.py#L689-L694"
