    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "This logic does not make any sense to me for n=0. It makes sense to skip weekend if n=1, but not not if n=0. Zero means zero, i.e. adding it should not change the input: a+0==a.\r\n\r\nIn your logic, zero is zero on weekdays, but it is one on weekends."
